flowchart LR
    A[Audio file<br/><i>mp3 / wav</i>] --> B[librosa DSP]
    B --> B1[beat tracking<br/>onset detection<br/>tempo estimation]
    B --> B2[HPSS<br/>harmonic / percussive split]
    B --> B3[section structure<br/>energy + repetition]
    A --> D[Demucs<br/><i>vocal stems</i>]
    D --> B3
    B1 --> R[(RhythmAnalysis<br/>+ SongPhase[]<br/>+ SongSection[])]
    B2 --> R
    B3 --> R
    R --> P[Prompt builder<br/><i>style-aware,<br/>section-aware</i>]
    P --> G[Gemma 4<br/><i>26B-A4B via cloud<br/>or E4B local</i>]
    G --> V[Verifier<br/><i>code re-grounds<br/>each line in DSP</i>]
    V --> O[Coaching output<br/>tutor + drills + transitions<br/>unified timeline]
    R -.-> V

    classDef dsp fill:#0e7490,stroke:#06b6d4,color:#f0fdfa
    classDef llm fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#f5f3ff
    classDef io fill:#1e293b,stroke:#475569,color:#f8fafc
    class B,B1,B2,B3,D dsp
    class G,P,V llm
    class A,R,O io
